@startuml 1.6 User edits his profile (client side and server side)
actor Client
participant IHMMain
participant Data
participant Communication
actor Server 

Client ->> IHMMain++: Modifie le profil



 
IHMMain -> Data++: updateProfil(client: Client)
Data --> IHMMain: void | Exception
deactivate IHMMain
Data -> Communication++: updateProfil(client: Client)
Communication ->> Server++: updateProfil(client: Client)
Communication --> Data: void | Exception
deactivate Data
Server ->> Communication: void | Exception
deactivate Server
deactivate Communication
    

@enduml
